CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 7, 2006

[Cite as 04/07/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-1731.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-1832. State ex rel. Bandlow v. LeBarron.

In Mandamus. This cause came on for further consideration of relators’ motion for relief from judgment. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion is denied.
